---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Adhésion - UDTL 31">
	<main class="pt-24">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="relative h-[720px] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-low">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
				<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90" alt="Flotte de camions alignés" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519003722824-194d4455a60c?q=80&w=2075&auto=format&fit=crop"/>
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-background via-background/80 to-transparent"></div>
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 w-full">
				<div class="max-w-3xl">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
						<div class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></div>
						<span class="text-primary font-headline font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">FORCE OUVRIÈRE HAUTE-GARONNE</span>
					</div>
					<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] text-on-background mb-8">
						VOTRE FORCE,<br/>
						<span class="text-primary">NOTRE UNION.</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl font-body text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
						Rejoignez l'UDTL 31 pour transformer l'isolement en action collective. Ensemble, nous bâtissons la forteresse de vos droits dans la Haute-Garonne.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<button class="signature-gradient text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-sm font-headline font-extrabold text-[15px] flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-all uppercase tracking-tight">
							Adhérer maintenant
							<span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
						</button>
						<button class="bg-surface-container-lowest/10 border border-outline text-on-background backdrop-blur-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-sm font-headline font-bold text-[15px] hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all uppercase tracking-tight">
							Découvrir vos avantages
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pourquoi nous rejoindre (Grid Section) -->
		<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-24">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter mb-4"><span class="border-b-[4px] border-primary pb-1">Pour</span>quoi nous rejoindre ?</h2>
			<div class="h-8"></div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 mb-8">
				<!-- Protection Juridique -->
				<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-lowest border-l-4 border-primary p-12 relative custom-shadow overflow-hidden">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">gavel</span>
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Protection Juridique Dédiée</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg mb-4">
						Accédez à nos experts en droit du travail pour chaque étape de votre carrière. Conseil, médiation et assistance juridique complète pour garantir vos droits face aux enjeux contractuels.
					</p>
					<!-- Giant ghost shield -->
					<div class="absolute -right-8 -bottom-12 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 300px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shield</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Solidarite -->
				<div class="md:col-span-4 signature-gradient p-10 flex flex-col justify-between text-on-primary rounded-sm">
					<div>
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary text-4xl mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">groups</span>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Solidarité<br/>Régionale</h3>
						<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-8">
							Intégrez un réseau puissant au cœur de la Haute-Garonne. Une communauté active prête à soutenir chaque membre dans ses luttes et ses projets.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
					   <div class="h-px bg-white/20 mb-4 w-full"></div>
					   <span class="font-headline font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Union Départementale 31</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
				<!-- Négociation -->
				<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface p-10 flex flex-col justify-center rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">handshake</span>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-white">Négociation<br/>Collective</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-surface-dim leading-relaxed">
						Nous portons votre voix lors des accords d'entreprise et de branche pour améliorer vos conditions de travail et de rémunération.
					</p>
					<div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 140px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">handshake</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Formations -->
				<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-high p-10 flex items-center justify-between rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="max-w-md relative z-10">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Formations Syndicales</h3>
						<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
							Maîtrisez les outils du dialogue social. Nous proposons des modules de formation exclusifs pour devenir un acteur clé au sein de votre entreprise.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1/3 bg-cover bg-center hidden md:block" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop'); clip-path: polygon(15% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); mix-blend-mode: multiply; filter: grayscale(100%);">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Form Section -->
		<section class="bg-surface relative py-24 mb-12">
			<!-- Visual split background -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 flex">
				<div class="w-1/2 h-full bg-surface-container-low"></div>
				<div class="w-1/2 h-full bg-surface"></div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16">
				<!-- Left: Formulaire -->
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
					<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 custom-shadow relative rounded-[2px]" style="box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(94, 63, 59, 0.08);">
						<!-- Decorative pink outline -->
						<div class="absolute -inset-4 border border-outline-variant/30 pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
						
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-black font-headline mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter">Formulaire d'adhésion</h3>
						<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-10 leading-relaxed">
							Rejoignez-nous en 3 étapes simples. Vos informations sont protégées et confidentielles.
						</p>

						<!-- Steps -->
						<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-10">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-headline font-bold text-xs">1</div>
								<span class="font-headline font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-primary">Identité</span>
							</div>
							<div class="h-px w-12 bg-surface-container-high"></div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center font-headline font-bold text-xs">2</div>
								<span class="font-headline font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Profession</span>
							</div>
							<div class="h-px w-12 bg-surface-container-high"></div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center font-headline font-bold text-xs">3</div>
								<span class="font-headline font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Cotisation</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<form class="space-y-6">
							<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
								<div>
									<label class="block font-headline font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">Nom</label>
									<input type="text" class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border-none border-b-2 border-outline/50 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 font-body py-3 px-4 transition-colors" placeholder="Votre nom">
								</div>
								<div>
									<label class="block font-headline font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">Prénom</label>
									<input type="text" class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border-none border-b-2 border-outline/50 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 font-body py-3 px-4 transition-colors" placeholder="Votre prénom">
								</div>
							</div>
							<div>
								<label class="block font-headline font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">Adresse E-mail</label>
								<input type="email" class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border-none border-b-2 border-outline/50 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 font-body py-3 px-4 transition-colors" placeholder="email@exemple.com">
							</div>
							<div>
								<label class="block font-headline font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">Téléphone</label>
								<input type="tel" class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border-none border-b-2 border-outline/50 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 font-body py-3 px-4 transition-colors" placeholder="06 00 00 00 00">
							</div>
							
							<button type="button" class="w-full bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface py-4 font-headline uppercase font-bold text-[13px] tracking-widest mt-6 hover:opacity-90 active:scale-[0.98] transition-all rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
								Continuer vers l'étape suivante
								<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_forward</span>
							</button>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Right: Info -->
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center pl-0 md:pl-10">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 border-l-4 border-primary pl-4">Vos données sont sacrées</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-10 text-sm">
						Conformément à nos valeurs de discrétion et de respect, votre adhésion est strictement confidentielle. Votre employeur n'en sera jamais informé par nos soins.
					</p>

					<div class="bg-surface-container-high p-6 rounded-sm mb-8 border-l-2 border-outline-variant/50">
						<h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-sm mb-2 text-on-background">Besoin d'aide ?</h4>
						<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-xs mb-4">Nos délégués sont à votre écoute pour vous accompagner dans votre démarche.</p>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-primary">
							<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">call</span>
							05 61 00 00 00
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="flex items-center gap-6 p-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-[2px] custom-shadow">
						<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-surface-container-high rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-white shadow-xl relative opacity-80 mix-blend-luminosity">
						   <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524661135-423995f22d0b?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-50"/>
						   <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
							  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline">map</span>
						   </div>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="font-headline font-black text-sm uppercase mb-1">UDTL 31</h4>
							<p class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant">93 boulevard de Suisse<br/>31200 Toulouse</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Bottom Giant text Block -->
		<section class="signature-gradient py-24 relative overflow-hidden text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-8">
			 <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-10 pointer-events-none mix-blend-overlay">
				<span class="font-black font-headline text-[20vw] whitespace-nowrap leading-none tracking-tighter" style="color: #410002;">FORCE<br/>OUVRIÈRE</span>
			</div>
			<div class="relative z-10">
			   <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black font-headline text-white italic uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight max-w-4xl mb-12" style="text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
				   "LA FORCE DU COLLECTIF, LA LIBERTÉ DE L'INDIVIDU."
			   </h2>
			   <button class="bg-surface-container-lowest text-primary px-10 py-5 rounded-sm font-headline font-extrabold text-[15px] hover:bg-surface transition-all uppercase tracking-widest shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/30 active:scale-95">
				   Adhérer aujourd'hui
			   </button>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
